{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>Alice和Bob玩了一个古老的游戏：首先画一个n × n的点阵（下图n = 3）<p><p>接着，他们两个轮流在相邻的点之间画上红边和蓝边：<p><p>![](pic/1347.gif)<p><p>直到围成一个封闭的圈（面积不必为1）为止，“封圈”的那个人就是赢家。因为棋盘实在是太大了(n ≤ 200)，他们的游戏实在是太长了！他们甚至在游戏中都不知道谁赢得了游戏。于是请你写一个程序，帮助他们计算他们是否结束了游戏？<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"格子游戏 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出一行：在第几步的时候结束。假如m步之后也没有结束，则输出一行“draw”。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入数据第一行为两个整数n和m。m表示一共画了m条线。以后m行，每行首先有两个数字(x, y)，代表了画线的起点坐标，接着用空格隔开一个字符，假如字符是\"D \"，则是向下连一条边，如果是\"R \"就是向右连一条边。输入数据不会有重复的边且保证正确。<p>","examples":"<input>3 5\n1 1 D\n1 1 R\n1 2 D\n2 1 R\n2 2 D\n</input><output>4\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1347","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}